---
title: Asian Sweet-Soy Beef & Broccoli Stir-Fry with Jasmine Rice & Spring Onion
description: We love a tender bit of broccoli in our beef stir-fry and we hope you’ll agree that it lends the perfect veggie touch to this one. We can’t forget the zing of the spring onion, because all these elements together help to make a stir-fry we simply adore.

*We’ve replaced the crispy shallots in this recipe with spring onion
due to local ingredient availability. It’ll be just as delicious, just follow your recipe card!*
